var storyContent = {"inkVersion":21,"root":[["#","^AUDIOLOOP: train1.mp3","/#","#","^MUSIC: test.mp3","/#","^You wake up alone in a subway car.","#","^IMAGE: 1_subway.gif","/#","\n","^The lights flicker overhead as the train sails through stations you do not recognize.","\n","^ANASAZI ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^SULVA BAY ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^The stations blur as you move past. You lunge toward the emergency brake, but hesitate trying to decide if you should stop immediately or wait for the next station.","\n","ev","str","^Pull the brake","/str","/ev",{"*":"0.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Wait for the next station","/str","/ev",{"*":"0.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"pull_brake"},"\n",{"->":"0.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"next_station"},"\n",{"->":"0.g-0"},{"#f":5}],"g-0":["done",{"#f":5}]}],"done",{"pull_brake":[["^Your hand flies to the yellow emergency brake.","\n","^I wouldn’t do that. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^A calm voice, coming immediately from your left side.","\n","^You spin around and find yourself staring at an older man. The burgundy suit he wears looks like it belongs from another time. Dust clings to his coat and to the tangled black and grey hair that half hides his face.","\n","^I didn’t know you were there ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^He tilts his head.","\n","^I’m always here. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^The train slows noticeably. You turn your gaze to the window as the train approaches the platform.","\n","ev","str","^BENNINGTON STATION ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":[{"->":"bennington"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"bennington":[["#","^IMAGE: IMAGE2.JPG","/#","^The sign glows pale green in the gloom of the tunnel.","\n","^I suggest you get back in your seat. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^But should you blindly do what this mysterious stranger says, or ignore his advice and get as far away from him as you can?","\n","ev","str","^Get back in your seat","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Get off?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"next_station"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"get_off"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"next_station":[["^The train slows at the station, but you've decided it's best to stay rooted to your seat. Through the window, figures appear on the platform. There are dozens of them, unmoving, dressed in dark, almost featureless uniforms. Their eyes are unreadable as they watch you through the glass.","\n","^The doors hiss open. No one boards and no one leaves.","\n","^Once the doors slide shut again, the train begins to move.","\n","^You turn to the man in the burgundy suit.","\n","^Who were those people? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^He smiles faintly, still watching the darkness outside.","\n","^Is that what you really want to know? ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^He glances at you now, eyes gleaming.","\n","^Or would you rather ask what’s waiting at the next station? ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","ev","str","^Who were those people?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^What happens at the next station?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"those_people"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"next_next_station"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"those_people":[["^The people on the platform… they're called the Laxaria League. They don’t take kindly to outsiders in their zone. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^Zone? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^A world carved out by electrical storms. Lightning that never sleeps, skies that never clear. They say the storms began when outsiders started crossing over. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^You stare at him, trying to make sense of it.","\n","^I don't understand. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^He leans back, gaze drifting upward.","\n","^You will. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","ev","str","^Ask for more information","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Ask about next station","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"more_info"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"next_station"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"next_next_station":[["^The man leans forward, the air around him suddenly heavier.","\n","^The next station is Marconi. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^Like the radio guy? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Exactly. A pioneer in more ways than most realize. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^You'll find things here a bit more ahead of your time, maybe even unnervingly so, but it's your best chance of returning. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^Returning? Returning where? Where am I? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^The old man just smiles, his expression unreadable. You're a bit fed up with his cryptic answers and you're not sure if you should bother to ask him anything else.","\n","ev","str","^Should you wait for Marconi station?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Or ask for more information","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"marconi_station"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"more_info"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"more_info":[["^I’m afraid you’ve slipped into a Transit Shift. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^A tunnel between dimensions. It’s rare, but not unheard of. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^You shake your head in confusion.","\n","^But, how did I get here? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^He pauses to take a deep breath.","\n","^We think it has to do with the level of consciousness at certain underground thresholds. Perhaps you dozed off and your mind slipped just enough. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^You honestly can't remember falling asleep, but he could be right.","\n","ev","str","^Keep listening","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"listening"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"listening":[["^There are many dimensions, but this particular tunnel only passes through five. It was accidently opened in 1953 during a massive energy collector test. Ever since, well... travelers like you occasionally slip through. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^I won’t bore you with the details. Your best chance to get back is at Marconi station. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^The lights flicker again and the train slows. Outside the window, a strange glow pulses along the walls of the platform.","\n","^MARCONI STATION ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","ev","str","^Get of at Marconi station?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Stay on","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"marconi_station"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"stay_on"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"get_off":[["^The train screeches to a halt. Before you can react, the doors hiss open and two uniformed men lunge forward, seizing you by the arms.","\n","^Off the train. Now! ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n","^You're yanked off the platform, shoes scraping against the floor. One of the guards, thick-necked and scowling, leans in close.","\n","^How'd you end up on this train? You with Flannan's crew? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^You stay silent, not sure what's happening.","\n","^Not talking? Then I’ll just hand you over to Sodder. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^He jerks his head and a new figure steps forward. This man is tall and lean. All shadow and sharp edges. This must be Sodder.","\n","ev","str","^stand still","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^run away","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"standstill"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"runaway"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"runaway":[["^You get no further than 2 steps before a hot pain bursts through your back. What were you thinking? You're not a runner. You don't even know where you are.","\n","^And now you'll never find out.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"runaway.0.4.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"runaway.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.4.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"standstill":[["^Without a word, Sodder grabs your arm and pulls you aside. In his unshakable grip, you're forced to follow him down a narrow corridor toward a heavy, industrial door.","\n","^The door glows red and radiates heat.","\n","^Sodder speaks, still facing the door, his voice low and even.","\n","^Behind this door lies a river of molten lava. We harness energy from the heat. Now, you can either talk to me or go through the door. ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","ev","str","^Talk to Sodder","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Go through door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"talk_to_sodder"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"go_through_door"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"talk_to_sodder":[["^I don’t know how I got here. I don’t even know where here is. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Sodder studies you with his cold gaze for a moment before speaking.","\n","^How did you end up on that train? ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","^I ride the train every day. I got on at Grand Central. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Grand Central!? As in New York? ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","^Yes! I must have dozed off because when I woke up, none of the stations looked familiar. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Sodder raises an eyebrow.","\n","^There is no New York. ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","ev","str","^What do you mean, no New York? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"nony"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"nony":[["^Unless you mean the New York Island Quarantine and Research Zone? ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","^I... I don’t understand. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Eyes, narrowing, Sodder steps back.","\n","^Did you break quarantine? Is that why you’re here? You might have infected us all! ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","^Before you can answer, Sodder seizes your arm. With the other hand, he yanks open the heavy metal door. A blast of heat slams into your face.","\n","^Without hesitation, you're shoved forward. You have no choice as you stumble forward.","\n","ev","str","^Go through the door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"go_through_door"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"go_through_door":[["^On the other side of the door, there is a river of lava. It snakes through the cavern floor, its surface bubbling and spitting out sparks. Two figures dressed in bulky heat suits operate a device, slowly siphoning lava into a thick, reinforced cylinder.","\n","^Suddenly, a woman rushes up from your right. She also wears a heat suit, but has removed her helmet.","\n","^Who are you? Where is your protective gear? ","#","^CLASS: lady","/#","\n","^I... I was pushed in here. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^She groans.","\n","^Great. Another one. Go down that tunnel to your left and pick up a suit in the supply room. ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","ev","str","^ Try to talk to the woman.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"dontmelt"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"dontmelt":[["^There's no time to talk! Hurry before you melt! ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","^She then quickly turns away, shouting instructions at the others.","\n","^You don't wait to argue. You break into a fast walk down the tunnel to your left. About a hundred feet in, you spot another metal door with “Supplies” stenciled in faded white paint.","\n","^Across from it, tucked low into the rock wall, is a second door. It's small, rusted and just barely tall enough to crawl through.","\n","ev","str","^Go through Supply door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Crawl through rusty door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"get_supplies"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"crawl_through_rusty_door"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"get_supplies":[["^It takes both hands to pull down on the heavy handle to the supply room door. With a loud clunk, the mechanism releases, and the door creaks open.","\n","^Inside, the room is dim and industrial, about the size of a two-car garage. The air is cooler here but still carries a metallic tang.","\n","^Lined neatly along the back wall are rows of heat suits, all separated by size.","\n","^To your left is a row of dented lockers, stretching along the wall.","\n","^To your right, there's another door. Closed and unmarked.","\n","ev","str","^Put on heat suit","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Go through the closed door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"heat"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"door"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"crawl_through_rusty_door":[["^You drop to your knees and pry open the small, rusty door. It’s difficult to see in the darkness, but there appears to be a passageway.","\n","^You quickly crawl inside. It’s a tight fit, but you continue forward. There is no way to turn around now.","\n","^Time blurs. After what feels like an hour, but is likely only about 15 minutes, you come to another door, rough and rusty like the first.","\n","ev","str","^You push it open and pull yourself through.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":[{"->":"door"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"door":[["^You spill out into a grimy alley, landing hard on the cracked pavement. Overflowing garbage cans line the walls, leaking into a large brown puddle that snakes toward the street.","\n","^The street!","\n","^You scramble to your feet and onto the main street, but something is wrong.","\n","^There are no cars. No people.","\n","^But there are signs.","\n","^CONDEMNED ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^QUARANTINE ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^Then, a deep thrumming overhead. A helicopter.","\n","ev","str","^Wave your hands to get their attention.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"wavehands"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"wavehands":[["^The chopper slows. For a moment, hope rises in your chest.","\n","^But then the hatch opens.","\n","^A burst of brownish-green gas erupts, raining down directly onto your position.","\n","^You gasp before you can think. The air turns heavy. Oily. Wrong.","\n","^Your knees buckle. The world swims.","\n","^The street fades.","\n","^Your body hits the pavement.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"wavehands.0.14.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"wavehands.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.14.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"heat":[["^You struggle into the extremely bulky heat suit, zipping it up to your neck and pulling the hood over your face. The hood has a built in transparent face, so you are able to see as you fasten the hood to your collar, creating a seal.","\n","^Once the suit is on, you exit back through the supply door where the woman who sent you there is waiting.","\n","^Even if you seem inexperienced, we need all the hands we can get. The energy tunnel is blocked. Some of the lava has cooled and turned to rock. Take this device and start siphoning out the lava so we can reach them. ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","ev","str","^Refuse to take the device.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^ Take the device.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"refuse"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"takedevice"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"refuse":[["^I don't have time for this. You put on the device now or I throw you in the lava. Got it?! ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","^This woman means business. You take the device and hook it over your shoulders in imitation of the other figures currently siphoning lava.","\n","^Now how do you operate this?","\n","ev","str","^ Walk up to a figure and wave for help.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"watchfigure"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"takedevice":[["^She hands you a contraption that hooks on to your shoulders and fits like a large backpack. There is a hose with a handle that can be removed from one side - to siphon the lava with, you deduce.","\n","^Not sure what else to do, you follow her instructions and head back down the hall to the cave where you saw the two figures holding the same contraption you now carry. You fall into line beside the largest one.","\n","ev","str","^Watch the largest figure and learn what to do","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"watchfigure"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"watchfigure":[["^Since talking with the protection suits would be near impossible, the large figure takes your side hose, places it in your hand and flips a switch on the upper part. They then guesture toward the lava and return back to their work.","\n","^Simple enough, you think.","\n","^You spend the next hour siphoning up the lava, surprised that the pack on your back doesn't melt or make you hotter than you already are. It's hard to imagine a material that could handle this. Also, what is happening to all the lava that goes inside? There's no way it could hold as much as you siphon off.","\n","^Your arms are starting to get tired. How long do you have to do this? Are you a prisoner here? What should your next move be?","\n","ev","str","^Plan an escape","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Wait and see what happens","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"escape"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"whathappens"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"escape":[["^You made it this far, but if you're doomed to work these lava tunnels for the rest of your life, you'll never get back home. It's time to take matters into your own hands.","\n","^Lifting the hose and turning off the power switch on the upper strap by your shoulder, the other figures turn their heads as you try to signal \"be right back.\" Though you have no idea if they get your meaning, when you point to your wrist. Do they even have watches here?","\n","^Either way, the figures seem satisfied and turn back to their work.","\n","^You remember the rusty door in the supply room. Maybe it's a way out? The only way to know is to try it.","\n","ev","str","^Go back down the hall","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"backdown"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"backdown":[["^Heading back down the hall, you're in luck. The woman in charge is nowhere in sight. You see the supply door and slip through before she can come out. Once inside, you unlatch your hood, unzip the jumpsuit and wiggle your way out, sweat pouring down your entire body.","\n","^The small, rusted door is in the corner. You drop to your knees and wrench it open. The darkness beyond is thick, but you catch a glimpse of a narrow passage.","\n","^No time to think.","\n","^You slide in headfirst. The space squeezes around you, forcing you forward. There's no room to turn back now.","\n","^After crawling for what must be at least fifteen minutes, you reach another door much like the first.","\n","^No way to go but forward. You push the door open.","\n","ev","str","^Go through the door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"door"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"whathappens":[["^You need answers and maybe the woman can help you. While you are trying to decide what to do and how to find her again, a loud horn blows, reverberating through the cave.","\n","^The two other figures shut down their devices. You hurriedly do the same, then turn to see the woman in her outfit. She makes a swirling motion with her hands, then turns and walks down the hall. The two others step in line behind her.","\n","ev","str","^ Follow ","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Try to escape","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"follow"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"tryescape"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"tryescape":[["^You see a small, rusted door is in the corner before the next turn. You hang back and once the woman and figures are out of sight, you run to the small door and wrench it open. The darkness beyond is thick, but you catch a glimpse of a narrow passage.","\n","^No time to think.","\n","^You slide in headfirst. The space squeezes around you, forcing you forward. There's no room to turn back now.","\n","^After crawling for what must be at least fifteen minutes, you reach another door much like the first.","\n","^No way to go but forward. You push the door open.","\n","ev","str","^Go through the door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"door"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"follow":[["^After a series of turns through the tunnels, the woman opens the door to a room with some worn couches and a table with jugs of water on top. Your companions and the woman lift off their helmets and you do the same. Everyone goes to the table to get a drink.","\n","^You lift the jug to your mouth but as the liquid goes in, you realize this isn't water at all. It's bitter, almost like vinegar. You choke, spitting the vile drink out from your mouth.","\n","ev","str","^I can't drink this! ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"cantdrink"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"cantdrink":[["^I thought there was something odd about you. Now that I take a closer look, I can see you're not from Gaea. The shape of your ears is wrong. Nor do I believe you're from the quarantined Earth or you wouldn't have managed to work for so long in the heat. Who are you? ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","^Relieved that someone has finally realized there's been a mistake, you explain everything and how you were pushed through the door by someone called Sodder.","\n","^Ugh, that brute. Always passing along his problems to someone else. Well, I do appreciate your help today, but this isn't where you should be. I'm sending you upstairs. Let's go. ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","^You follow the woman out of the room, through a corridor and to an elevator. She escorts you in, pushes the button that reads FLOOR 1 and then steps back out.","\n","^Good luck ","#","^CLASS: sodder","/#","\n","ev","str","^Continue in the elevator up to Floor 1","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"reception"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"reception":[["^You step out of the elevator into a large room. The walls are obsidian-black and the floor beneath your feet is polished marble.","\n","^You approach a glass desk, behind which sits a woman with sharp eyes and an unreadable expression.","\n","^You face the woman, and tell her you're lost. She stares, so you continue:","\n","ev","str","^Where am I?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"Where_am_I"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"marconi_station":[["^The train glides to a halt and the doors slide open.","\n","^You step out into a spectacular silver hall carved into the heart of an enormous cavern. Light dances around the metallic surfaces, reflected from unseen sources above.","\n","^Your companion walks ahead, his footsteps echoing as he strides toward a set of towering double doors across the gleaming floor. You follow, your own steps strangely muted.","\n","^The next chamber is smaller, but no less striking. The walls are obsidian-black and the floor beneath your feet is polished marble.","\n","^The man leads you to a glass desk, behind wich sits a woman with sharp eyes and an unreadable expression. He tilts his head in your direction.","\n","^Another lost traveller. ","#","^CLASS: suit .","/#","\n","^The woman nods once and beckons you forward. The man in the burgandy suit turns to you once more.","\n","^This is where I leave you. Good luck on your journey. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^And without another word, he exits back the way he came.","\n","^You face the woman, your voice unsure, and ask:","\n","ev","str","^Where am I? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Who was that man? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"Where_am_I"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"thatman"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"stay_on":[["^The man exits the train, but you stay behind.","\n","^The doors slide shut with a hiss and the train lurches forward, picking up speed.","\n","^The air gets hotter. Lights flicker overhead. On the display panel, a single phrase blinks in red:","\n","^END STATION ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^As the train nears its final stop, you see them. Rows of cages lining the platform.","\n","^Inside are people dressed in clothing from every era of the last century. Suits, bomber jackets, dusty jeans. Their faces are hollow, eyes unfocused.","\n","^Their guards, part human and part machine, move among the cages like zookeepers.","\n","^One of them, the biggest of all, turns toward your train car, eyes gleaming in excitement.","\n","^You should have gotten off at Marconi station.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"stay_on.0.21.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"stay_on.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.21.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"Where_am_I":[["^You've found your way to the city of Electra. We're located deep underground. This is a community of scientists, researchers and explorers. Some of us are descendants of the original founders, while others have made their way here through years of study... or by accident. I assume you fall into the latter category. ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","^You nod slowly, still trying to catch up. She continues.","\n","^If you came by train, then it's likely you passed through one of our hidden gateways. Your companion is one of our field researchers – a dangerous job. He travels between the four Earth Divisions, gathering external data and maintaining contact. ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","ev","str","^Four Earth Divisions? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"fourearth"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"fourearth":[["^She pauses, studying you for a second.","\n","^Yes, and I need to know which one you're from. Just to confirm, can you name your oceans? ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","^You stare, unsure if you heard correctly.","\n","^Oceans? Um... Pacific, Atlantic, Indian… ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^That’s good. You’re close to your own world. Perhaps Landini can help. ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","^She gestures toward the rear wall.","\n","^Take the elevator. Floor 2. Let the floor attendent know you need to see Landini. ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","^You hesitate, then walk toward the elevator barely outlined in the shining back wall. The doors slide open as you approach. You glance back once and enter.","\n","^The doors seal shut behind you. A soft chime sounds, and a number pad lights up on the panel beside you.","\n","ev","str","^Floor 1","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Floor 2","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"floor_1"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"floor_2"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"thatman":[["^That's one of our field researchers. It's a dangerous job. He travels between the four Earth Divisions, gathering external data and maintaining contact. ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","^Four Earth Divisions? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Yes, Earth A, B, C and D. ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","^How do I know which one I'm from? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^That's easy, just name your oceans! ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","^My oceans? Do you mean Pacific, Atlantic, Indian... ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Perfect. That means you're close to your original world. You should talk to Landini. ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","^The woman then points to the elevator located on the wall behind her.","\n","^Floor 2. ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","^Um, thanks. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^You make your way to the elevator. Once inside, you're met with two buttons on a panel.","\n","ev","str","^Floor 1","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Floor 2","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"floor_1"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"floor_2"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"floor_1":[["^The doors open immediately. You're still in the same hall. The woman at the glass desk turns with a frown on her face and asks","\n","^Is there a problem? ","#","^CLASS: reception","/#","\n","^You shake your head to apologize and push","\n","ev","str","^Floor 2","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"floor_2"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"floor_2":[["^You feel a sudden shift, your body lifting up at an incredible speed. The sensation lasts barely three seconds before fading, leaving you on steady ground again. The doors before you slide open revealing a man in a gleaming red suit standing in the threshold. Behind him, a long hallway stretches, it's smooth blue walls shimmering faintly in the light.","\n","^He eyes you sharply.","\n","^What is your business here? ","#","^CLASS: redman","/#","\n","^You shift your weight from one foot to the other, trying to steady your nerves.","\n","^Uh, I need to see Landini. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^He meets this statement with a sharp nod.","\n","^Follow me ","#","^CLASS: redman","/#","\n","^He turns and starts walking.","\n","ev","str","^Follow him","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"followhim"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"followhim":[["^The hallway is quiet. No doors or windows break the sleek design. It's just an endless stretch of blue walls. After only twelve steps, the man stops. He places one hand against the wall, and with a soft hum, a doorway materializes in front of you.","\n","^You step inside.","\n","^The room beyond is dimly lit, books scattered across a desk in a deliberate mess. A woman sits behind it, her eyes scanning you with quiet curiosity.","\n","^I was told to speak with you about getting home. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Landini doesn’t react immediately. Her gaze sweeps over you, studying you in a way that feels both calculating and thoughtful. Finally, she gestures toward the empty chair in front of her desk.","\n","^And home would be Earth, Gaea or Zanius? ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","ev","str","^Earth","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Gaea","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^Zanius","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"earth"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"gaea"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"zanius"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"earth":[["^And your ocean names? ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^You let out a frustrated sigh.","\n","^Why do you all keep asking? Pacific, Atlantic... ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Landini's lips curl into a small, knowing smile.","\n","^That will do. I just needed to confirm which Earth you were from,  Earth A or Earth B. Looks like you’re an A. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^What is Earth B? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Landini frowns.","\n","^An Earth that lost its way. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^You stay silent as Landini gathers her composure, her earlier hardness gone.","\n","^But you’re from Earth A, which is good news. If you wish to return home, I think we can handle that. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","ev","str","^ How? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"how"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"how":[["^She gestures to the books behind her.","\n","^The answer lies within the Archive of Truths, a repository of knowledge that spans across all dimensions we’ve encountered. These books contain information on the different dimensions and worlds we've discovered so far. Identify the information that matches your world, and it will open an entryway back home. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^An entryway? Where is the entryway? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Landini smiles and shrugs her shoulders.","\n","^Out in the hall you just came from. Find the correct code and the entryway will open. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^You think a minute and then respond:","\n","ev","str","^How do I begin? ","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Can't you just do it for me? ","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"howdoibegin"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"doitforme"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"howdoibegin":[["^Landini stands and walks toward the towering shelves of books behind her. She selects a large volume bound in an unidentifiable sleek, green material. She turns, offering it to you.","\n","^You take it with a mixture of hesitation and expectation. The moment your hands make contact, the book seems to hum slightly in your grip, like it’s aware of you.","\n","^As you open it, you expect pages, but instead, the surface ripples and rearranges. The \"book\" isn’t a book at all. It's some kind of interactive system. You stare down at the glowing surface.","\n","^You ask:","\n","ev","str","^How does this work?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"howwork"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"howwork":[["^It’s the interface to the Archive of Truths. Each book is a gateway to knowledge. They store the truths of each dimension, but not all truths fit every world. You’ll need to prove your ability to discern what’s real and what isn’t. If you make the right connections, it will reveal the path you need. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^How am I supposed to know how to answer this? There’s no keypad. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","ev","str","^Ask Landini for help","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"bookhelp"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"bookhelp":[["^Landini gives you a knowing look, almost like she’s seen this before.","\n","^Look closely for the inconsistencies, the anomalies. The ones that don’t belong. Your Earth, your home, will have information that only you will recognize. When you are ready with the answer, speak it aloud. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^A soft hiss behind you. The door you came through slides open. Standing in the threshold is the man in the gleaming red suit, standing perfectly still.","\n","^Thomas will escort you back to the lobby. You may take as long as you need to solve your puzzle. I wish you luck in what you seek. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","ev","str","^ Follow Thomas ","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^ Why can't I stay here? ","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"followthomas"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"whycant"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"whycant":[["^Landini shakes her head.","\n","^This is a journey you must take alone. Now follow Thomas to the lobby. Once there, open the book again. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","ev","str","^ Follow Thomas ","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"followthomas"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"followthomas":[["^Still reeling from everything you’ve just heard, you nod mutely. Clutching the open book, you turn and follow Thomas out into the corridor. As soon as you step past the threshold, the door behind you dissolves without a sound. Now there is only a smooth, seamless wall.","\n","^You both head back toward the elevators, where you now notice two sets of couches you paid no attention to before. Without speaking, Thomas indicates that you should sit on one of the couches. You do as he says.","\n","^Once seated, you look down at the screen in the book again. The page reads:","\n","^HOW DO YOU KNOW YOU ARE REAL?","\n","^You answer out loud:","\n","ev","str","^I can feel the floor under my feet and the book in my hands.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^I think, therefore I am. ","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^I don’t. ","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"feel"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"think"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"dont"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"feel":[["^The glowing question fades, replaced by a slow ripple of light across the screen. The sensation under your feet intensifies briefly, almost like the floor is acknowledging you.","\n","^ACKNOWLEDGED. ROOTED IN THE PHYSICAL. INITIAL PHASE CLEARED. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^So, the book acknowledges you are a physical being with awareness in the immediate present, you think to yourself.","\n","^A soft ding sounds from the book in your hands. The response has disappeared, and a new text is forming.","\n","ev","str","^PROCEED TO VERIFICATION","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"proceed"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"proceed":[["^The screen dims. Your surroundings melt into colorless fog and then solidify again, reshaping into a cozy, Earth-like room.","\n","^You’re standing in a study, lit by warm lamplight. A small table sits in the center, holding three items:","\n","^1. A steaming mug of black coffee.","\n","^2. A pair of worn knitted gloves with dirt stains on the fingers.","\n","^3. The book “The Wonderful Wizard of Oz”, publishing date 1900.","\n","^Each item looks perfect. Familiar. Comforting. But there’s a catch. You can feel it.","\n","^ONE OF THESE BELONGS TO YOUR REALITY ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^The Archive's electronic voice emanates from all around you.","\n","^THE REST ARE APPROXIMATIONS. YOU MUST CHOOSE THE TRUE ARTIFACT. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","ev","str","^Examine the coffee","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Examine the gloves","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^Examine the book","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"examinecoffee"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"examinegloves"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"examinebook"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"examinecoffee":[["^You reach toward the mug first. The warmth feels right. But the smell isn’t bitter enough. It smells sweet, like it was recreated by someone who’s never actually tasted coffee.","\n","ev","str","^Examine the gloves","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Examine the book","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^Finished examining. Move on.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"examinegloves"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"examinebook"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"finishexam"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"examinegloves":[["^The gloves are brown, stitched with uneven stripes. You recognize them as a pair your mother made for you as a child. In fact, you remember that she used to get so angry with you because you would wear them to dig in your backyard. You ease one of the gloves open and slip your hand in. Perfect fit.","\n","^You take the glove off and set it back on the table.","\n","ev","str","^Examine the coffee","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Examine the book","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^Finished examining. Move on.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"examinecoffee"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"examinebook"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"finishexam"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"examinebook":[["^The last item you inspect is “The Wonderful Wizard of Oz.” Of course, you’re familiar with the film, but you’ve never seen a copy of the book this old. You pick it up to examine the pages and illustrations. As you flip through, you see the familiar mentions of Auntie Em, Glinda the Good Witch and Dorothy’s silver slippers. Wait. Silver?","\n","ev","str","^Examine the coffee","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Examine the gloves","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^Finished examining. Move on.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"examinecoffee"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"examinegloves"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"finishexam"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"finishexam":[["^After thinking about all three for several minutes, you choose:","\n","ev","str","^The coffee","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^The gloves","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^The book","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"coffee"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"gloves"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"book"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"coffee":[["^I choose the coffee.","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^You figure this entire thing is probably a trick question.","\n","^Suddenly, the room disappears. You are back in the lobby with lights flashing all around. A speaker begins to blare","\n","^Alert: Earth B resident in the facility! Apprehend immediately! ","#","^CLASS: alarm","/#","\n","^Thomas, the man in red, is quickly at your side, twisting your hands behind you while a contingency of guards come jogging toward you from the hall.","\n","^Take him into custody! ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n","^Two guards grab you with gloved hands at your shoulders and shove you down the hall where a red door has suddenly appeared.","\n","^Without saying a word, they rip open the door.","\n","ev","str","^They shove you in, slamming it shut behind you.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"door"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"gloves":[["^You pick up the gloves. This is what is intimately connected to you. You recognize that your mother made them.","\n","^I choose the gloves. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^The room around you suddenly disappears. You are back in the waiting room facing the hallway. A door down the way has appeared, glowing orange.","\n","^You excitedly make your way to the door, open it and enter without hesitation. The door shuts behind you and disappears.","\n","^Immeditately, you find yourself gasping, skin slick with fluid and a hospital gown clinging to your shoulders. Around you, other naked adults blink under bright white lights, stretching like newborns.","\n","^Ah! There you are. ","#","^CLASS: mom","/#","\n","^A woman in a floral apron rushes toward you, clutching a thermos. It's your mother, her smile wide and familiar. You'd recognize her anywhere.","\n","^You’ve been playing outside again, haven’t you? ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^You stare at her.","\n","ev","str","^Mom? ","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"mom"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"mom":[["^She reaches up on her tiptoes and brushes your wet hair back.","\n","^Don’t you ‘Mom’ me, youngster. You’re late for dinner. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^You look around. Rows of incubation vats hum quietly behind glass walls. Inside: floating, unmoving adults. All the same age. All waiting?","\n","^A nurse walks by holding a clipboard, nodding politely.","\n","^New release? ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n","^Mine. Fresh out this morning. Already causing trouble. ","#","^CLASS: mom","/#","\n","^With a shock, you realize this is not your world, and there's no way back.","\n","^Well, at least you have your mother.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"mom.0.25.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"mom.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.25.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"book":[["^The coffee doesn't smell right and you've realized that the gloves your mother made would have fit you as a child, but these fit you as an adult. Those things can't be right. It must be the book. You know the book came out before the movie, so it's possible the movie portrayed things differently.","\n","^The book ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^VERIFICATION EARTH A, BETWEEN DIMENSIONS 34-52. IN THESE DIMENSIONS, THE SHOES IN THE BOOK ARE SILVER WHILE THE SHOES IN THE FILM ARE RUBY. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^You breathe a sigh of relief as the room begins to fade away. However, you don't find yourself in the lobby, but in:","\n","ev","str","^another room.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"anotherroom"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"anotherroom":[["^This room is all white, and you're standing in the middle.","\n","^PUT THE BOOK ON THE FLOOR ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^You do so.","\n","^NOW ANSWER THESE QUESTIONS AS QUICKLY AS POSSIBLE. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^1. WHAT IS THE SHORTEST MONTH ON YOUR PLANET? ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","ev","str","^February","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^September","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"February"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"September"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"February":[["^28-29 DAYS. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^2. HOW LONG DOES IT TAKE FOR YOUR EARTH TO ROTATE? ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"February.0.10.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^12 hours ",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"February.0.11.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^24 hours ",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"February.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.10.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],{"->":"twelve"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"February.0.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.11.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],{"->":"twentyfour"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"twelve":[["^A 12 HOUR ROTATION FITS EARTH C, A PLANET OF EXTREMES. HERE IS YOUR DOOR HOME. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^A door appears before you. What did he mean by extremes and Earth C? It IS a 12 hour rotation, right? You never paid much attention in Science class.","\n","^Inside the room, you can see what looks like some sort of concrete bunker. Is that the basement to your apartment building? Could be. Whichever way, you just want to get out of here. You step through the door.","\n","ev","str","^Step through the door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"extreme"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"extreme":[["^The door slams shut behind you and you find yourself in a large concrete bunker, about the size of an airplane hanger. There are people, shops and dim lighting. You wonder where you are.","\n","^An agitated man runs forward to you.","\n","^Did you oversleep again? It's your turn to go out with the team for supplies! Get suited up! ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n","^He thrusts a snow jumpsuit at you as thick as an astronaut's suit.","\n","^What's this about? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Have you lost your mind? You volunteered for this. Every month a team goes to the surface to collect supplies. Everyone knows it's not safe outside with the global blizzard. Now get up there before you're docked rations! ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n","^So that's what was meant by \"extremes.\" This isn't your Earth at all. Why didn't you listen more at school?","\n",["ev",{"^->":"extreme.0.23.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"extreme.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.23.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"twentyfour":[["^24 HOUR ROTATION. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^FINAL QUESTION. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^WHAT IS EMPATHY? ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","ev","str","^I don't know","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Being able to understand and share feelings with others.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"dunno"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"feelings"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"dunno":[["^A WASTE OF A SPECIES. YOU MAY RETURN TO EARTH B, WHERE YOU ARE CLEARLY FROM. GOOD RIDDANCE. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^A door appears in front of you. You don't like the sound of that \"Good riddance.\" But perhaps the people here just have different values than back home. You do wonder, however, if you misunderstood the question.","\n","ev","str","^Return to Earth B","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Ask to change your answer","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"earthb"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"newanswer"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"earthb":[["^You can't wait to be out of here. You step swiftly through the door and it disappears immediately behind you.","\n","^Looking around, you realize you've been dropped by the side of the road in a desert. How will you get home from here?","\n","^A car approaches in the distance. You wave your hands to get its attention. It speeds past. After a few moments, a truck appears. You wave your hands again, but the driver throws an empty bottle out the window and it hits you on your head, causing you to bleed.","\n","^Now, with blood pouring from your head, you are sure someone will stop to pick you up, but no one does. 60 cars pass and no one stops.","\n","^You eventually pass out from loss of blood and thirst. Every few hours, you wake enough to crack open your eyes, just to see more cars speed by, completely ignoring you.","\n","^This world lacks any empathy whatsover. As you close your eyes for the last time you wonder if this was your original world or not. It's hard to tell.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"earthb.0.12.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"earthb.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.12.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"newanswer":[["^I misunderstood the question. Can you ask again? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^WHAT IS EMPATHY? ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","ev","str","^Being able communicate with your mind","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Being able to understand and share feelings with others.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"mind"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"feelings"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"mind":[["^YOU ARE THINKING OF TELEPATHY. ARE YOU ABLE TO DO THIS OR ARE YOU SIMPLY AN UNINTELLIGENT BEING? ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^Oh, right. You were thinking of telepathy. But do you want to admit you were wrong or should you save face and pretend you have telepathy?","\n","ev","str","^Admit you were wrong","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Say of course you can speak through minds!","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"admit"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"telepathy"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"admit":[["^I'm sorry, you're right. I was confusing the word. I meant to say that empathy means being able to understand and share feelings with others. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^IT TAKES A BRAVE PERSON TO ADMIT MISTAKES. AND BECAUSE YOU KNOW EMPATHY, I NOW KNOW WHERE YOU BELONG. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^A door opens in front of you. It looks like your old apartment inside. You walk through the door.","\n","ev","str","^walk into your apartment","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"walkin"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"walkin":[["^The apartment looks just as you left it. You're so relieved to be back home with comfortable sights and smells. You never realized how much you love your everyday life.","\n","^Suddenly the phone rings. You answer. It's your best friend.","\n","^You're back! You're alive! We've all been so worried! ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n","^You start to wonder how long you've been gone. It was only a day in your head.","\n","^How long have I been gone? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^It's been a week! Your parents have put out a missing persons report. The rest of the group and I have been searching everywhere for you. Where were you? ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^You won't believe it but I.... um.... ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^You remember the train, but everything else is a blank. You have this feeling you were somewhere extraordinary. That you've been through an amazing experience, but you just can't seem to remember.","\n","^It seems some things in life remain a mystery, but at least you have people who care about you.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"walkin.0.30.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"walkin.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.30.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"telepathy":[["^AMAZING. THIS IS ENTIRELY NEW FOR YOUR SPECIES. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^The room you're in turns back into the lobby area. Suddenly, an alarm sounds. Within minutes, a team of scientists and two security guards arrive in the elevator.","\n","^SUBJECT IS READY FOR STUDY ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^We've been waiting to discover someone with telepathy for a long time. These guards are here to escort you to our neurological facility where we will do some intensive studies on your brain. But don't worry, it should only take a few years and then we will see about returning you home. ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n","^You are grabbed firmly by the security guards and pulled toward the elevator. You start to speak, but a scientist immediately puts an adhesive device over your mouth.","\n","^No no! It's best to just communicate telepathically for our studies. See you downstairs! ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"telepathy.0.24.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"telepathy.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.24.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"feelings":[["^YES, NOT ALL WORLDS HAVE THIS CONCEPT. I KNOW WHERE YOU BELONG NOW. GOOD LUCK TO YOU. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^A door opens in front of you. It looks like your old apartment inside. You walk through the door.","\n","ev","str","^walk into your apartment","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"walkin"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"September":[["^17 DAYS HATH SEPTEMBER. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^THIS EARTH DIED OUT OVER 500 YEARS AGO. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^CARE TO TRY AGAIN? ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","ev","str","^February","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"February"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"think":[["^The glowing question fades, replaced by a slow ripple of light across the screen. You feel a warm glow from your hands, holding the book. Not too hot, but comfortable.","\n","^CLASSIC PHILOSOPHICAL ORIGIN DETECTED. HIGHER-ORDER REASONING CONFIRMED. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^The text disappears directly after you’ve read it and is replaced by a second question.","\n","^IF YOU ARE REAL, WHAT IS HOME? ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","ev","str","^Two doorways appear in front of you.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"twodoors"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"twodoors":[["^Both doorways are open.","\n","^Through one, you can see your apartment. It hasn't been clean in a while. It's dark and lonely. The old couch in the corner is covered in stains.","\n","^Beyond the other door is a beautiful kitchen, with marble floors and high-tech devices. In fact, it's the kitchen you've always dreamed of. Light shines through a large window. This place looks welcoming. Could you just walk into this life?","\n","ev","str","^Walk through your old apartment door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Walk through the fancy kitchen door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"apartment"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"kitchen"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"kitchen":[["^Your old life wasn't really all that great when you think about it. Why not invent a new life for yourself? One with all the modern conveniences in a fancy apartment.","\n","^But this is amazing! Whatever this world is, it can't be that bad if you've ended up in this fancy apartment.","\n","^As you're admiring the softness of the huge, velvet couch in your living room, you hear a door slam.","\n","^Honey, I'm home! ","#","^CLASS: nice","/#","\n","^Do you live with someone now? Well, they have a nice voice. Maybe you really got lucky this time!","\n","ev","str","^But then another voice answers.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"anothervoice"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"anothervoice":[["^This voice is annoyed and gruff.","\n","^Sorry about the mess, but I just got home and the slave hasn't cleaned our quarters yet. ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n","^Slave?","\n","^Two sets of footsteps angrily stomp toward the living room. You realize the voices don't belong to people. Not even to humans. What stands before you are immensely tall grey beings with scaly skin and sharp teeth. Their large eyes look angry, reflecting your terrified face.","\n","^Why haven't you cleaned the apartment, human?! Get to work or it's back to the mines for you! ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n","^Maybe your old life wasn't that bad after all. Too bad you got greedy.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"anothervoice.0.18.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"anothervoice.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.18.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"apartment":[["^You walk through to your old apartment. It's not the most comfortable place, but it's home, and that's all you want is to go home.","\n","^Once you walk through, the door behind you seals, becoming a wall again. The apartment is covered in dust, much more than it should be since you've only been gone about a day. In fact, the entire apartment has a smell of rotting food.","\n","^You walk over and look out the window. The leaves are falling off the trees. It was full summer when you got on the subway yesterday. How much time has passed?","\n","^There's a knock at your door. Do you open it?","\n","ev","str","^Open the door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Ignore the door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"opendoor"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"ignoredoor"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"opendoor":[["^You open the door and are met by a familiar face. Your old friend from the subway car. His black and grey hair is still messy and tangled, but his burgundy suit is more modern than last time you met. He smiles.","\n","^Just checking in, my friend. How are you adjusting? ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^I just got here, but I think I've been gone a long time. How long has it been? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Well, about two months have passed since you boarded the subway. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^Two months?! I had a job! I must be behind on my rent! ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","ev","str","^What happened? ","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"happened"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"happened":[["^Well, crossing dimensions and worlds isn't an exact science. You should honestly be happy you got back at all. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^Anyway, I came here not just to check on you but to also ask you a question. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^You're too stunned to respond. He continues.","\n","^Would you be interested in joining me in my work? It's basically keeping tabs on the other worlds, a few alternate dimensions here and there. Interested? ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","ev","str","^Yes","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^No","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"Yes"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"No"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"Yes":[["^You look around at your dusty apartment. What do you have to lose?  The job was a dead end and you were never really attached to your apartment anyway.","\n","^After the adventure you just had, your eyes are open to a world - no, worlds - of possibility.","\n","^Yes, why not? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^I'm glad to hear it. Let's start right away. Come with me. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^He gestures out to the hallway.","\n","^Do I need to take anything? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Nope, you'll have new clothes, unlimited food budget. Almost anything you want, really. Just come with me. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^I never caught your name. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^You exit your apartment for the last time, closing the door.","\n","^You can call me James. I got into this business a lot like you, but I fell asleep on a bus instead of a subway. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^I'd like to hear more about that. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Sure thing. But for now, we have a train to catch. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"Yes.0.48.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"Yes.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.48.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"ignoredoor":[["^That's probably someone with questions and you don't have your head together enough to answer them. Best to figure things out first.","\n","^Luckily, your electricity is still working. You turn on the television to a national news station.","\n","^QUARANTINE ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^The message flashes at the bottom of the screen.","\n","^You watch as the newscasters talk about entering the third year of quarantine, discussing the evacuation of major cities and everything people had to leave behind.","\n","ev","str","^A map appears","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"map"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"map":[["^Of course, your city is marked the map. You didn't think about it before, but when you looked outside, there were no people. That didn't make sense, but there was no time to dwell on it.","\n","^The news continues, saying that satellites have picked up live figures in some places, but scientists speculate anyone who did not evacuate before the quarantine would be highly dangerous to others as the disease affects the brain, leading to violent tendencies.","\n","^And we all recall the breakouts in that first year, before we understood what was happening and got the majority of people to safety. I sure wouldn't want to be trapped in a quarantine zone. It's basically a death sentence. ","#","^CLASS: nice","/#","\n","^Whoever is at your door knocks again.","\n","^And again.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"map.0.13.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"map.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.13.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"No":[["^I appreciate the offer, but I just need to get back to normal. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Not a problem. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^By the way, I never caught your name. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^You can call me James. I got into this business a lot like you, but I fell asleep on a bus instead of a subway. ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^And you never went back? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^James smiles.","\n","^Never had much to go back to. Wife was gone. Made it through a war just to be stuck in a community home. Nah, I'm more for an adventure. Are you sure you don't want to come along? ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","ev","str","^Ok","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^No thanks","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"Yes"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"nothanks"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"nothanks":[["^I think I've had enough adventure to last me a lifetime. Thanks anyway. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Well, it's your choice. Good luck out there. You'll need it! ","#","^CLASS: suit","/#","\n","^And with that, James walks down the hall and turns the corner.","\n","^I'll need it? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^What does he mean?","\n","^You close the door and head back into your dusty apartment.","\n","^Luckily, your electricity is still working.","\n","ev","str","^Turn on the television","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"turnontv"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"turnontv":[["^A national news station is on the screen.","\n","^QUARANTINE ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^The message flashes at the bottom.","\n","^You watch as the newscasters talk about entering the third year of quarantine, discussing the evacuation of major cities and everything people had to leave behind.","\n","^A map appears on the screen marking the cities affected.","\n","ev","str","^Look at the map","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"maplook"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"maplook":[["^Of course, your city is marked on the map.","\n","^The news continues, saying that satellites have picked up live figures in some places, but scientists speculate anyone who did not evacuate before the quarantine would be highly dangerous to others as the disease affects the brain, leading to violent tendencies.","\n","^And we all recall the breakouts in that first year, before we understood what was happening and got the majority of people to safety. I sure wouldn't want to be trapped in a quarantine zone. It's basically a death sentence. ","#","^CLASS: nice","/#","\n","^You frantically run out of the apartment, bursting into the hall.","\n","^Wait! James! James! ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^James doesn't answer, but someone else does. They're laughing. It's a high-pitched laugh, maniacal.","\n","^Is there someone here now to play with? I'll be right up! ","#","^CLASS: angry","/#","\n","^You run back into your apartment, slamming the door behind you.","\n","^Looks like you're going to have an adventure whether you like it or not.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"maplook.0.27.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"maplook.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.27.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"dont":[["^The light on the screen freezes for a second, then ripples, as if the system itself is… processing. There’s a pause, longer than before. Not silence, but anticipation.","\n","^COGNITIVE DISSONANCE ACKNOWLEDGED. EMOTIONAL DEPTH: ELEVATED. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^The screen clears, and in its place appears a mirrored surface, your own reflection staring back, blinking in real-time. But there’s something...off. Your face begins to change.","\n","ev","str","^ Look at your reflection","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"lookreflect"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"lookreflect":[["^First you see yourself looking polished, in a designer suit. A bit nicer than you usually appear.","\n","^Next, the image changes. You are wearing glasses, surrounded by books. Your image appears scholarly. All-knowing.","\n","^Finally, the surface changes again and you are looking at your own, familiar face.","\n","^WHO ARE YOU? ONLY ONE OF THESE REPRESENTS YOUR TRUE SELF. CHOOSE WISELY. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","ev","str","^Choose the polished, designer suit you.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Choose the wise, scholar version of yourself.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^Choose your familiar, dull face.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"suit"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"scholar"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"face"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"suit":[["^This is your chance to better your life. No one knows anything about you. This you has a fancy suit, and probably a lot of money. The screen on the book goes dark and a door appears in front of you. It opens to a state-of-the-art kitchen space, with large windows and a spacious living room behind. You set the book down gently and walk through the door.","\n","ev","str","^Step though the door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"kitchen"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"scholar":[["^The second version is me. I'm a wise scholar. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^The screen on the book blinks. Writing appears.","\n","^RETURN ME TO THE OFFICE. ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^Alright, I guess I'm done. I'll just give the book back to Landini and she'll show me which door to go through.","\n","ev","str","^Return the book","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Change your answer","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"returnbook"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"changeanswer"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"returnbook":[["^You walk back to Landini's office. The door is open and you find Landini at her desk, a curious expression on her face. You hand her the book and you notice the screen blip with new text as she takes it. After a moment of reading the screen, she looks up and smiles.","\n","^So you've decided to join us here! You seek knowledge and want to research all worlds! This is so exciting. We haven't had a new recruit in ages. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^This isn't what you wanted. You open your mouth to speak, but before you can get a word out, Landini speaks.","\n","^Honestly, I'm relieved. Between you and me, we've never managed to actually get anyone back to their original home. I was wishing you luck, but I knew the chances were low. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","ev","str","^Low?! ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"low"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"low":[["^So you could have ended up in a different world? What wrong with these people?","\n","^I completely understand why you're upset. But the good news is that this can be your first assignment. Figuring out how to correctly relocate those who wander here accidently. It only took us 32 years to figure out how to get people to the right world. Maybe you'll be faster at getting them to the right dimension! ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^It looks like you have a long road ahead of you.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"low.0.9.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"low.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.9.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"changeanswer":[["^Wait! I didn't mean to say the second version. I meant to say: ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","ev","str","^I'm the rich guy in the suit.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^The last one is me.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"kitchen"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"face"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"face":[["^This is my face and it may not be perfect, but out of the three, it's the one I recognize. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^A WISE CHOICE ","#","^CLASS: sign","/#","\n","^The screen on the book fades to black and a door appears before you. It opens, and you see your old, familiar apartment. You set down the book and start forward toward the door.","\n","^Suddenly, Landini is back, out of breath from running to the lobby.","\n","^Wait! ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^You turn, confused.","\n","^I'm glad you found the way back to your world. It doesn't always work for everyone. But before you step through the door, do you really want to go back to your old life, or do you want to discover what it is we do here. The knowledge that we hold? ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","ev","str","^Go home","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Ask more","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"home"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"askmore"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"home":[["^I'm sorry, but this entire adventure just makes me more certain that I like the life I have. Other worlds and dimensions are just too much for me. In fact, I'm hoping in time, I'll forget this entire thing ever happened. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^With that, you step through the door.","\n","^And you're in your old apartment. It's like no time has passed. Everything is exactly how you left it.","\n","^You breathe a sigh of relief.","\n","^Your life goes on the same as before. No more surprises or strange adventures.","\n","^As the days, months and years go by, you find yourself noticing more in the news. Stories of mysterious disappearances that no one can explain. People claiming they crossed into another world. These tales are dismissed. There's always crazies out there.","\n","^And sometimes you wonder if you made the right choice.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"home.0.17.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"home.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.17.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"askmore":[["^So what is this place exactly? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Landini pauses, as if to collect her thoughts and then explains.","\n","^You've heard of old tales of lost cities, right? ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^Sure, El Dorado, Atlantis, Z. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Well, they aren't just old tales. There are many so called \"lost\" cities, but the truth is, they are simply hidden. For centuries, societies have been set up to find people described as geniuses or adventurous explorers, and they are invited to these places. No one knows when they were discovered, but most seem to contain pockets that can transport a person to a parallel Earth. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","ev","str","^Like Gaea or Zanius or Earths A-D? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"likethose"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"likethose":[["^Right! The first two seem to be quite old and have spun off in a different direction than some of the other Earths we've come across. We just use letters for those. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^You look at Landini for a moment.","\n","^I'm not sure if you're having me on, if you're crazy or if this is real. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^I understand it can be a bit overwhelming. You still have a choice to go back to your own world. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^She then gestures toward the open door of her office, where you see a new door. It opens and you can see your apartment on the other side.","\n","^I think it's best if I ... ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","ev","str","^Go back to my old life ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Learn a bit more ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"home"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"learnmore"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"learnmore":[["^Occasionally, people like yourself accidently slip through. There's still some pockets we haven't discovered. Many disappearances in history have happened because of this. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^You're intrigued.","\n","^So those stories I hear where people just turn a corner or don't come back from the store, or even go into a building and never come out? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Sometimes that's what happens. You've probably even heard some of the names. Many choose to stay. Some go back but are kept under watch to protect our secret. The man who brought you in here on the train. That's part of his job. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","ev","str","^The man in the burgundy suit? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"theman"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"theman":[["^Yes ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^So I could do something like that? Visit other worlds plus my own? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Landini gives a sad smile.","\n","^Technically, yes, but it's reserved for those who are well trusted and have been with us for a very long time. We're all about trust and secrecy, you know. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^I understand. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^You're a little disappointed, but also intrigued.","\n","^Landini looks you in the eye.","\n","^You have a decision to make. Give up your old life and join us here or go back home and keep our secret. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","ev","str","^Join Landini","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Go back to your old life","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"join"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"home"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"join":[["^You've been looking for adventure all your life. What do you have to go back to? A lonely apartment? A dead-end job?","\n","^I'll join you. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","^Landini embraces you excitedly.","\n","^Oh, I have so much to show you. What are you interested in first? The record of extraterrestrial encounters? The real meaning of the Voynich Manuscript? What we use the Nazca Lines for? ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^As she links her arm around yours and starts walking you down the hall, you realize that you're about to live an amazing life. What a shame you can't tell anyone.","\n",["ev",{"^->":"join.0.16.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"join.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.16.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"doitforme":[["^She chuckles.","\n","^My dear, I’d love to, but I can’t. Even though you’re from Earth A, there are countless variations. I could never guess which one is yours. That's the task of the Archive. Only you can decipher the truth, recognize the path that leads home. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^Ok, then. ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","\n","ev","str","^How do I begin? ","#","^CLASS: main","/#","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"howdoibegin"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"gaea":[["^Well this is excellent news! We've been looking for a Gaean for quite some time. One of our energy tunnels has been blocked and the heat is too intense. We could use your assistance in clearing it. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^Without another word, she springs from her desk, her movements sharp and purposeful. As she strides toward the door, you can almost feel the shift in the air. Something urgent is at play.","\n","^She glances back at you as you fall in step behind her.","\n","^I’ll escort you as far as sub-level 5. From there, you’ll need to navigate the seven tunnels to reach the blockage. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","ev","str","^Change your answer to Earth","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Change your answer to Zanius","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},"ev","str","^Go to sublevel 5","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"earth"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"zanius"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"sublevel"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"zanius":[["^Landini pulls a small device from her pocket, her movements swift and precise. With a flick of her wrist, a sharp green ray shoots out, striking your chest. The sensation is immediate. Your body begins to dissolve, the skin cracking and fading like dust in the wind.","\n","^As the world around you distorts, her voice cuts through the haze, icy and detached.","\n","^Good riddance. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"zanius.0.9.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":2},{"s":["^Try again from the beginning.",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"zanius.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.9.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","#","^RESTART","/#","end",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"sublevel":[["^Landini accompanies you to the elevator where you ride down in silence to sub-level 5. The doors open and a blast of heat enters the elevator.","\n","^Good luck navigating the tunnels. Just follow the tunnels that branch off with the color red and don't go down any tunnels with another color. ","#","^CLASS: landini","/#","\n","^She gives you a stern push out of the elevator and the doors close behind you.","\n","^Nothing to do now but follow the tunnels.","\n","^There aren't that many tunnels that branch off and you follow the red ones. After the sixth tunnel, there is one more branch. A short red tunnel leading to a set of doors reading LAVA RIVER and a blue tunnel with a tiny, rusty service door you would need to crawl into.","\n","^Which one should you take?","\n","ev","str","^LAVA RIVER door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},"ev","str","^Tiny service door","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"go_through_door"},"\n",{"#f":5}],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"crawl_through_rusty_door"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}};